name: Mavis Dracula
description:
Mavis from Hotel Transylvania. Always was a fan of this cutie.

Unfortunately, this may be my last upload for some time. My 3090 is fried and this is the last LORA I have finished. Feel free to ping me on Discord if you want any of my datasets.

Still keeping my Ko-Fi open for now. No pressure to give anything, but it may help get me get back up and running sooner.
